      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:8:21:10",
      "text": [
        " مَا تَخَتَّمَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) إِلَّا يَسِيراً حَتَّى تَرَكَهُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Ali Bin Atiyya, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> did not wear a ring except for a little while, until he<sup>saww</sup> left it’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "10. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Ali ibn ‘ Atiyyah who has said the following: “Abu ‘ Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said that the Messenger of Allah used the ring for a very little time and then he (the Messenger of Allah) abandoned it.’” "
        ]
      }
